{"tid":1320978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新城市廣場地契確有警察通行條款","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:14:04.000Z","uid":10540,"like":7,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3715f0a253487c240dfc4a98bfd7b46d6a7fd7de","tid":1320978,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67065067_2503095036617477_5867696088282038272_n.png?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_oc=AQniWzfJt7t9tR-64fCJ-sFp3iCBarXoLcK01fA7xbb-bwwK-zsUopMR3_anpEmqP2k&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=31a827a7592b47658bd528fe49af6ef7&amp;oe=5DBE7DF7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67065067_2503095036617477_5867696088282038272_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_oc%3DAQniWzfJt7t9tR-64fCJ-sFp3iCBarXoLcK01fA7xbb-bwwK-zsUopMR3_anpEmqP2k%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D31a827a7592b47658bd528fe49af6ef7%26oe%3D5DBE7DF7&h=85252c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚有警察進入新城市廣場執行職務, 令管理公司引來批評, 另有一番爭議. 翻查於新城市廣場於1981年嘅地契 (STTL 143), 入面的確寫有較少見嘅地契條款, 就係&quot;Police Access&quot; 同埋&quot;Police Report Centre&quot; 條款 (圖1). &quot;Police Report Centre&quot; 條款之後於1984年取消, 但&quot;Police Access&quot; 則保留. 如根據地契, 管理公司的確不能阻止警察進入.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66712690_2503112749949039_6931788233164455936_n.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQmQ4u6MFi-UeN6bPjfvoewYU0wsMkS-YD-facNZRErvU14T2bHxiQkDBiMwDlIyO4c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=e98b1411c8ae11b66ef88bf3b2325c56&amp;oe=5DB5B253\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66712690_2503112749949039_6931788233164455936_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQmQ4u6MFi-UeN6bPjfvoewYU0wsMkS-YD-facNZRErvU14T2bHxiQkDBiMwDlIyO4c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3De98b1411c8ae11b66ef88bf3b2325c56%26oe%3D5DB5B253&h=8f431c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他地契相關條款<br />\n<br />\n另外要留意返, 小編亦想補充返今朝關於警察進入私有產權地方嘅post, 部份屋苑地契亦會因應&quot;公眾空間&quot;而包含 &quot;警察通行條款&quot; (如圖2) 容許警察進入&quot;公眾空間&quot;執行職務... 如想知道自己屋苑地契有無類似條款, 則可到&quot;田土廳&quot;查冊及搵專業人士提供意見.<br />\n<br />\n當然, 地契條款並唔係法例, 而係契約. 除地契外, 一切亦要跟隨法例處理.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGPSURVEYOR/posts/2503125239947790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGPSURVEYOR%2Fposts%2F2503125239947790&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjfPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=bbbd8b9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGPSURVEYOR/posts/2503125239947790</a>"},{"pid":"f34c8cd0601164caca273a31c81163462a031558","tid":1320978,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"be9be34793932af95b216308d42b29818df06439","tid":1320978,"uid":73340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"88 新城市廣場"},{"pid":"4d3215f2a564fd9da67322b78e2ec48883bdf230","tid":1320978,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78c8d9b089e00562607decab16057238c8f5521a","tid":1320978,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"仲有咩商場有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51483ead0a607c08c0ff466bb4ed06b0375b60a","tid":1320978,"uid":35474,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:38:50.000Z","msg":"歷史文件仲有效力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"22b22d858426a22554c197f6157eb9f5d014e4b8","tid":1320978,"uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4ba8066ebe0a4932b8e156086cb6d7f39852a1","tid":1320978,"uid":167506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/